Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.13,0:03:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  和不與我們一組嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為規定是四個人一組
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕音部的成員作為一組去逛不是比較開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.44,0:03:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然可能會很辛苦  但唯就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪  澪  快點拍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:51.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點  以富士山為背景
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律也在啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連律也在啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.05,0:03:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺到一股視線…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都到了  京都到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要遺忘東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.71,0:04:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是京都啊  小律
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看  要在京都站坐巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金閣寺咧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯咧  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然到了京都  就要玩只用關西腔說話的遊戲咧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯咧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員都到齊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組長要好好確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼讓我們坐下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不對  是坐下來咧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是清點人數吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候一定會有人不見的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不給周圍的人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要排好隊伍走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完就睡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個無憂無慮的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律  那個是什麼  好像蘿蔔一樣哎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這裡也有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快點上車
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～好累
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是吃完了就睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來吃這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律  快點  這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:16.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  閃閃發光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  那個真的是用金子做出來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不對  做出來的嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯…咧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想稍微帶回去一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…這樣想是不行的…咧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被警察抓住…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住的下場…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:44.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…下場咧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經膩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（這一段我敢保證是京Ani專門為紬的聲優壽美菜子所設的，\N這是相當瞭解sphere的人才會理解的啊～ by TJX）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說金閣寺  曾在昭和25年被燒掉過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的是重新建起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,供奉釋迦牟尼骨灰的舍利殿的金閣非常有名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才被叫做金閣寺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其實好像是叫鹿苑寺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  看看  能喝抹茶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那種苦苦的茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有零食吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就和平時的放學後沒什麼兩樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:18.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又沒什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去喝吧  去喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.58,0:06:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就來喝喝看吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:24.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:33.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在茶會上喝抹茶的時候  要先吃零食再喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來抹茶的苦味會被釣出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不應該說什麼「哎」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律也該稍微學學這種上等的禮儀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得沒錯  很沒品哦  小律
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很低品  很粗俗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪不到你來說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:57.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北野…天滿宮？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:06:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很有名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:05.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神社的話在學校附近也有的說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡一定有大佛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.23,0:07:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的神在學問方面的祈福很出名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對備考的學生來說是很有名的神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  這個神社到處都有牛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣摸牛的頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭腦就會變聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  好啊好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是頭好牛  是頭很棒的牛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來摸你了  讓我變聰明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎  這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會遭到報應的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:39.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律  有繪馬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  繪馬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  唯  這也是某種紀念  所以來寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  把我們的願望傳達給神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  繪馬  繪馬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛  牛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛  牛～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:07:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會被拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.53,0:07:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:03.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我…一個祈福姻緣的護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.24,0:08:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  600日元
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊  天神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.71,0:08:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請實現我們的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.33,0:08:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現少女那小小的願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會實現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會實現就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請實現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:27.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  忘了投錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  那就再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你們在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是故意的嗎  嗚嗚～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…小佐和  你誤會了  誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是想實現寫在繪馬上的願望…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  只是想叮囑神實現我們重要的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.47,0:08:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找理由也沒門  到這裡來！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:46.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}一輩子都能吃得飽飽的  平澤唯\N能考上志願的學校  秋山澪\N能在武道館演出  田井中律\N希望能考上志願的學校  琴吹紬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～累死了～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  出了一身冷汗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.52,0:08:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  先換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:08:59.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～好麻煩～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼「好麻煩」啊  你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一點時間  先喝杯茶去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是帶來什麼玩的東西就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.41,0:09:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撲克的話我有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.06,0:09:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩這個怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大富翁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我知道那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是用各種手段成為大富豪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就邊吃零食邊來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊成～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會好好吃飯的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要剩飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們已經吃飽了嗎  好浪費啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微休息一下嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會全吃完的嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:53.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪的頭髮好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.77,0:09:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:10:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了冬天乾燥會很麻煩…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…紬的也很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是燙的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:06.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  這是自然卷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～  我也留長髮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣會變得像女孩子嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  唯！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.15,0:10:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前發怪物～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你在想像什麼啊  不准笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還想長高嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  我一定要長大給你看…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:39.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  差不多要關燈了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  我已經設好鬧鐘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也要早起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  琴吹同學幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等…唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.61,0:10:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  扔枕頭大戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡已經是戰場了  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  吃我這個魔球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再來吧…啊  痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好重的球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點睡！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.23,0:11:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬  戰鬥還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.34,0:11:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  熄燈了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿足啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小燈泡也得熄了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骷髏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:29.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（髑髏(しゃれこうべ)與洒落神戶(しゃらこうべ)發音相近）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:41.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Lycopene{\r}\N番茄紅素
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:41.84,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（番茄紅素(リコピン)與彈額頭(デコピン)發音相近）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,番茄紅～素
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬  豬鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:22.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  大家都到齊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是自由行動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各組按照預定的參觀路線行動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事記得打老師的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是六點前一定要回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.47,0:13:39.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就看到那家店在大拍賣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:42.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才買了那麼多零食啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:43.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.74,0:13:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆給我回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…我們這組是去嵐山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們打車去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  能節約時間  這樣比較…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…咦  唯和律呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  首先是這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:06.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼來京都還要去樂器店？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.79,0:14:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小氣鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等回家後再去就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就看一下下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我不管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.68,0:14:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這裡還有左手款式的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是嵐山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多店舖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人也好多～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那我們先去渡月橋…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讚啊！猴園誒！快看！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  猴子？有猴子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說到京都來看什麼猴子啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯！律！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到啦～到頂峰啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  這景色真不錯呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:15:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  這裡全是京都嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到能看到這麼好的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  那邊的休息所裡好像能餵猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用怕啦  看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一點都不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～猴子太滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.65,0:15:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  看  有特產
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哎  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  要給梓喵買點東西回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  就留她一個人留守
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:54.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就挑點有京都風味的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都風味？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.44,0:15:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.21,0:15:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:15:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:00.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～看了不少東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本還打算多逛點有名的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.85,0:16:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過今天錢包是用不著擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  買了這麼多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.02,0:16:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為什麼有那麼多錢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是給家人帶特產的錢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.47,0:16:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:26.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真給忘了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  時間差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.93,0:16:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回酒店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去坐電車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  車站在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.40,0:16:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.95,0:16:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你迷路了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒迷路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還看了那麼久地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在確認
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:51.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好癢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好  坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:16:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打攪一下咧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡怎麼到車站的誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.97,0:17:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…去車站的話  沿著那條路直走到頭右轉就是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？麻煩您啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽懂啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你！小律
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  知道怎麼走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  完全沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這邊  跟我來～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.06,0:17:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是知道這裡是哪裡就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  梓喵？我們現在迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給梓打電話有什麼用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是唯她們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:17:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  澪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.50,0:17:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  和和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  知不知道怎麼去車站啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.86,0:18:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你們也迷路了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不過那邊是北  走這條路應該沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著和和就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:16.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊該左轉吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.69,0:18:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按這條路走下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到原來的地方來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再看一遍地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骷髏…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骷…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好趕上吃晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  別讓人這麼操心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起～的咧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飯的咧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是貝司手秋山的咧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.28,0:19:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍不住了…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你們兩個  已經很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回房去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安  小佐和老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.84,0:19:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.07,0:19:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就該回去了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不過還有一個晚上…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  熄燈了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  太開心了～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就老老實實睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.51,0:19:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚還很長呢  小澪～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.51,0:19:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手！放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵—死—人—了—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:20:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不趕緊睡覺怎麼行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敗了敗了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你們出來旅行也這副德性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.36,0:20:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素顏的小佐和比平常恐怖10倍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？我沒聽清楚啊？再講一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早點睡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和也一起來聊天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你…人家是老師哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  就一會會嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.31,0:20:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有零食哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.14,0:20:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又想這樣把我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是因為你們幾個  搞得其他學生也都開始叫我小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給人的印象一落千丈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.15,0:20:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧我還裝那種賢淑溫柔的老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不該邀她來…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已經是三年級了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕音部再過一年就結束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想和大家繼續把樂團組下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.31,0:21:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續…下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.23,0:21:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山中老師？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嚇死我了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊  那本書已經有了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果就給弟弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯！富士山！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.90,0:21:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  哪裡哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.59,0:21:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我也要看…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉地上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪和我一樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.46,0:21:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.97,0:23:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕上了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.42,0:23:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有打電話回來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.62,0:23:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是趕上集合時間了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.21,0:23:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經到車站了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.64,0:24:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了…


